          <title>Federal Appeals Panel Pauses Order Restricting Access to Sensitive Data</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A federal appeals panel on Monday paused an order curtailing the Department of Government Efficiency's (DOGE) access to troves of sensitive personal data from three federal agencies, reopening the floodgates for the cost-cutting advisory board.]]></description>
